---
import LegalLayout from "../layouts/LegalLayout.astro";
import { site } from "../config";

// TODO(owner): the policy was supplied with this email; unify with config if needed.
const policyEmail = "liviraelegants@gmail.com";
const waDigits = site.whatsapp.replace(/\D/g, "");
---

<LegalLayout
  title="Return & Replacement Policy"
  description={`Return, replacement and refund policy for ${site.name}.`}
>
  <p>
    At <strong>{site.name}</strong>, customer satisfaction is our priority. Please read
    our Return &amp; Replacement Policy carefully before placing your order.
  </p>

  <h2>1. Returns &amp; Replacements</h2>
  <p>
    We accept returns or replacements only if the product received is
    <strong>damaged, defective, or incorrect</strong>.
  </p>
  <p>To be eligible:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>The issue must be reported within <strong>48 hours of delivery</strong>.</li>
    <li>
      The product must be unused, in its original condition, and with all original
      packaging intact.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>2. Non-Returnable Items</h2>
  <p>
    Due to hygiene reasons and the delicate nature of fashion jewellery, we do not
    accept returns or replacements for:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Change of mind</li>
    <li>Personal dislike or preference</li>
    <li>Used or worn products</li>
    <li>Products damaged due to improper handling or misuse</li>
    <li>Slight variations in colour caused by lighting, photography, or screen settings</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. Return &amp; Replacement Process</h2>
  <p>To request a return or replacement, please share the following:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Order Number</li>
    <li>A clear unboxing video (<strong>mandatory</strong>, without cuts or edits)</li>
    <li>Clear photos showing the issue</li>
  </ul>
  <p class="contact-block">
    <strong>Contact us:</strong><br />
    Email: <a href={`mailto:${policyEmail}`} class="link-underline text-champagne">{policyEmail}</a><br />
    WhatsApp: <a href={`https://wa.me/${waDigits}`} class="link-underline text-champagne">{site.whatsapp}</a>
  </p>

  <h2>4. Replacement</h2>
  <p>If your request is approved:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>We will replace the damaged or incorrect product, subject to stock availability.</li>
    <li>
      If the same product is unavailable, we will offer a suitable alternative or
      process a refund.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>5. Refund Policy</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Refunds are applicable only if a replacement cannot be provided.</li>
    <li>
      Approved refunds will be processed to the original payment method within
      <strong>5–7 business days</strong>.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>6. Order Cancellation</h2>
  <p>
    Orders cannot be cancelled once they have been confirmed, as we begin processing
    them immediately. Please review your order carefully before completing your
    purchase.
  </p>

  <h2>7. Important Note</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>
      An unboxing video (without cuts or edits) is <strong>mandatory</strong> for all
      damage, defect, or wrong item claims.
    </li>
    <li>Claims submitted without proper proof may not be accepted.</li>
    <li>
      {site.name} reserves the right to reject any claim that does not meet the above
      conditions.
    </li>
  </ul>
</LegalLayout>
